data.output: During one night at my local gym i bumped into Vin Diesel who commented on my abilty to lift my weight correctly. He decided to show me a better way to get my pump on. Whilst given the chance to ask him, i quipped if he had any siblings named after petrol.

My partner the bedroom window open during the night to let some cold air in, upon doing so a massive spider scurried in through into the bedroom. This would usually send my partner into a panic but this time she grabbed a letter and gathered it up into a glass and threw it outside. Normally she would send me to stamp on it.

Whilst walking home i was kidnapped by 3 men who demanded i chose an organ to have them harvest. I was very reluctant to agree and tried not to comply with the demands. They began to explain to me the reaches of their empire and that i best agree.

In order to fill my pokemon card collection i was missing the character Gloom, i maanged to locate a seller online who was asking for payment. I deciced to pay the asking price as that card was thought not to exist.
